org.nlpcraft.model

Class NCModelProviderAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nlpcraft.model.NCModelProviderAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, NCModelProvider

    public class NCModelProviderAdapter
extends Object
implements NCModelProvider
    Convenient model provider adapter. This provider takes one or more pre-created data models and will return them from makeModel(String) method. Sub-classes or client classes should call one of the following methods to pass data model instances this adapter will return:
    • setup(NCModel...)
    • setup(Collection)
    See Also:

      • setup

        public void setup(NCModel... models)
        Sets up this provider with given model instances. This method can be called multiple times to initialize the provider with different data models. On each call previous data models will be cleared.
        Parameters:
        models - Model instances.

      • makeModel

        public NCModel makeModel(String id)
        Description copied from interface: NCModelProvider
        Gets fully initialized model instance for given model ID. Note that this method can either create new model on demand or reuse the existing (cached) one if it is safe to do so.
        Specified by:
        makeModel in interface NCModelProvider
        Parameters:
        id - Unique, immutable ID of the model to make.
        Returns:
        Fully initialized model instance or null if provider does not support model with given ID.
        See Also:
        NCModelDescriptor.getId()

      • getDescriptors

        public List<NCModelDescriptor> getDescriptors()
        Description copied from interface: NCModelProvider
        Gets the list, possibly empty but never null, of model descriptors supported by this provider. Note that getting list of descriptors separately from the models themselves allows to query the provider without actually creating any models which can be an expensive process with side effects.
        Specified by:
        getDescriptors in interface NCModelProvider
        Returns:
        List of model descriptors supported by this provider (possibly empty but never null).
